{"title":"Singular Cycles Peregrine Mk 4 Frameset Pre-Order","link":"https://theradavist.com/singular-cycles-peregrine-mk-4-frameset-pre-order/","date":1748274649000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The latest batch of the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/singular-cycles-peregrine-review/\" target=\"_blank\">highly lauded</a>, all-steel, fat tire <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/singular-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Singular Cycles</a> Peregrine (<a href=\"https://singularcycles.com/products/peregrine-mk-4-frameset\" target=\"_blank\">£1200 frame and fork</a>) is due to land in the UK and US next week and will start shipping in the first week of June…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_04.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_04.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_04.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_04.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Peregrine utilizes a classic silhouette with all the demands of a modern gravel bike: full 29″ tires, quality steel, and all the fittings you need whether touring or commuting…</p>\n<p><strong>Classic design</strong><span>—the Peregrine uses a lugged frame and fork construction, which provides</span> both strength and a classic look.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_02.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_02.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Slender steel</strong> – slim tubing provides not just a classic aesthetic, but gives a supremely smooth ride. The Peregrine is no noodle, though; load it up and it feels solid and stable.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_05.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_05.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Big clearance </strong>– with space for up to 29×2.2″ (700×55 mm) tires and full-length mudguards.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Eccentricity is good</strong> – the Peregrine has an eccentric bottom bracket shell. This primarily benefits tensioning single cog drivetrains – whether fixed gear, singlespeed, or an internally geared hub. However, it is also really useful for fine-tuning the bottom bracket height when using different size wheels and tires – for instance, switching between 700c and 650b wheels.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_01.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Keep ’em outside</strong> – All cables are routed externally to the frame with neat modular cable guides. This makes maintenance and parts-swapping a breeze.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_06.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Singular_Perefrine_MK-4_Frame_06.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This new shipment of Peregrines has limited stock, so if you’d like to finally try one, roll on over to <a href=\"https://singularcycles.com/products/peregrine-mk-4-frameset\" target=\"_blank\">Singular Cycles</a> to check them out. And if you’d like a deeper dive, or stoop, into what makes the Peregrine such a fun platform, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/singular-cycles-peregrine-review/\" target=\"_blank\">read John’s review</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/singular-cycles-peregrine-mk-4-frameset-pre-order/\">Singular Cycles Peregrine Mk 4 Frameset Pre-Order</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"3b53031a07acb36ae68cb96005c3621542ed257d488d4b8878156dc433f2b4ed","category":"Cycling"}